      "author": "BiancaT (Bianca Taylor)",
      "cookedHtml": "<h2><a name=\"p-152534-weve-revamped-the-automation-builder-check-out-its-new-capabilities-below-arrow_double_down-1\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-152534-weve-revamped-the-automation-builder-check-out-its-new-capabilities-below-arrow_double_down-1\"></a>We’ve revamped the automation builder - check out its new capabilities below <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/arrow_double_down.png?v=15\" title=\":arrow_double_down:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":arrow_double_down:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></h2>\n<h4><a name=\"p-152534-without-leaving-the-automations-builder-you-can-do-the-following-2\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-152534-without-leaving-the-automations-builder-you-can-do-the-following-2\"></a>Without leaving the automations builder, you can <strong>do</strong> the following:</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/white_check_mark.png?v=15\" title=\":white_check_mark:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":white_check_mark:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" />  Delete, enable, disable, duplicate, and add a description to the automation recipe</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/5/e/5e0ab85af8967439967bb08028c84cf72e04131c.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.31.52 am\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/5/e/5e0ab85af8967439967bb08028c84cf72e04131c_2_690x299.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.31.52 am\" width=\"690\" height=\"299\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.31.52 am</span><span class=\"informations\">2522×1096 227 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h4><a name=\"p-152534-from-the-automations-builder-you-can-view-3\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-152534-from-the-automations-builder-you-can-view-3\"></a>From the automations builder, you can <strong>view</strong>:</h4>\n<p><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=15\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> who created the recipe<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=15\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> when the recipe was last updated<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=15\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> the connected app/integration<br />\n<img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/eyes.png?v=15\" title=\":eyes:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":eyes:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /> the automation ID</p>\n<p></p><div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/original/3X/0/0/00687fdd52fee74ba198d904afd3e4b4e47ccefc.png\" title=\"Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.33.28 am\"><img src=\"https://global.discourse-cdn.com/monday/optimized/3X/0/0/00687fdd52fee74ba198d904afd3e4b4e47ccefc_2_690x335.png\" alt=\"Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.33.28 am\" width=\"690\" height=\"335\" /><div class=\"meta\"><span class=\"filename\">Screen Shot 2023-11-08 at 10.33.28 am</span><span class=\"informations\">1594×776 40.4 KB</span></div></a></div><p></p>\n<h3><a name=\"p-152534-is-there-anything-thats-missing-that-youd-like-to-see-included-in-the-automations-builder-we-are-all-ears-4\" class=\"anchor\" href=\"#p-152534-is-there-anything-thats-missing-that-youd-like-to-see-included-in-the-automations-builder-we-are-all-ears-4\"></a>Is there anything that’s missing, that you’d like to see included in the automations builder? We are all ears!</h3>"
